window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>A stranger in town... </i></p> <p><i>A young waitress murdered... </i></p> <p><i>A Marine unleashed... </i></p> <p>Daniel Briggs, fresh out of the Marine Corps, wakes up in Defuniak Springs, FL, hungover and confused, with no memory of the night before. A powerful local family finds him, intent on repaying the previous night's encounter. </p> <p>How will the former Marine ward off his attackers, deal with his demons, and avoid being blamed for a young girl's death? </p> <p>This is Daniel's story from before his time with Cal Stokes and the rest of the team at Stokes Security International (SSI).</p>"; 
